snippet.title: Holdfast: Nations At War - Linebattle 2.0! Customisation & Progression
snippet.description:
Fall into line and ready your musket with the release of Linebattle 2.0! Featuring player progression and customisation, the sergeant, new animations and much more.
- Steam Store (65% OFF): https://store.steampowered.com/app/589290
- Grenadier Regiments DLC: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2107250

Join us on Discord. Play now.
https://discord.com/invite/holdfastgame

Song: "The Girl I Left Behind Me"
Vocalist: Molly Aisha - https://open.spotify.com/artist/1w0zFXIigI5poHt62DRGoJ
Composer: Komario
Producer: Anvil Game Studios
